  "rationale": "<p>Taking the square root of both sides of (x \u2212 1)\u00b2 = 16 gives x \u2212 1 = 4 or x \u2212 1 = \u22124. Solving each gives x = 5 or x = \u22123. Of the choices, 5 is a possible value.</p>"
